\c 31
\s UJoshuwa uzathatha isikhundla sikaMozisi
\p
\v 1 UMozisi wasehamba wakhuluma lamazwi kuIsrayeli wonke,
\v 2 wathi kubo: Ngileminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amabili lamuhla\x + 34.7. Eks. 7.7.\x*; kangiselamandla okuphuma lokungena\x + Nani 27.17.\x*. LeN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kimi: Kawuyikuyichapha le iJordani\x + 3.27. Nani 20.12. 27.13.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, yona izachapha phambi kwakho, yona izachitha lezizizwe zisuke phambi kwakho, ukuze udle ilifa lazo. UJoshuwa, yena uzachapha phambi kwakho\x + 9.3.\x*, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\x + 3.28. Nani 27.21.\x*\nd*.
\v 4 LeN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza kuzo\x + 3.21.\x* njengokwenza kwayo kuSihoni lakuOgi, amakhosi amaAmori, lelizweni lawo, ewachithileyo\x + Nani 21.23,24,33,35.\x*.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* izazinikela-ke phambi kwenu, ukuze lenze kuzo njengokwemilayo yonke engililaye yona\x + 7.2.\x*.
\v 6 Qinani, lime isibindi\x + 7,23. 3.28. Josh. 1.6,7,9. 10.25. 1 Lan. 22.13. 28.20.\x*, lingesabi, lingatshaywa luvalo ngenxa yazo\x + 1.29; 7.18,21; 20.3.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, yiyo ehamba lawe\x + 20.4.\x*; kayiyikukulahla, kayiyikukudela\x + 31.8. Josh. 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 7 UMozisi wasembiza uJoshuwa, wathi kuye phambi kwamehlo kaIsrayeli wonke: Qina, ume isibindi; ngoba wena uzangena lalababantu elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyise ukubanika lona; uzabenza badle ilifa lalo\x + 31.6,23.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, yiyo ehamba phambi kwakho; yona izakuba lawe\x + 9.3. Eks. 13.21.\x*, ingakulahli, ingakudeli; ungesabi\x + 31.8. Josh. 1.5.\x*, ungakhathazeki\x + 1.21; Josh. 1.9. 8.1. 10.25. Dute. 7.18.\x*.
\s Umlayo uzabalwa ekupheleni kweminyaka eyisikhombisa
\p
\v 9 UMozisi wasewubhala lumlayo, wawunika abapristi, amadodana kaLevi\x + 17.18.\x*, ababethwala umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*, lakubo bonke abadala bakoIsrayeli\x + 31.25. Nani 4.15. Josh. 3.3. 8.33. 1 Lan. 15.15.\x*.
\v 10 UMozisi wasebalaya esithi: Ekupheleni kweminyaka eyisikhombisa, ngesikhathi esimisiweyo somnyaka wenkululeko\x + 15.1,2,9.\x*, emkhosini wamadumba\x + Levi 23.34.\x*,
\v 11 lapho uIsrayeli wonke esefike ukubonakala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho endaweni ezayikhetha\x + 16.16.\x*, uwubale lumlayo phambi kukaIsrayeli wonke endlebeni zabo\x + Josh. 8.34,35. 2 Kho. 23.2. Neh. 8.1-3.\x*.
\v 12 Buthanisa abantu, abesilisa labesifazana labantwana, lowemzini wakho ophakathi kwamasango akho, ukuze bezwe, lokuze bafunde, bayesabe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, bagcine ukwenza wonke amazwi alumlayo\x + 4.10.\x*.
\v 13 Labantwana babo abangaziyo\x + 11.2.\x* bezwe, bafunde ukuyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, zonke izinsuku zokuphila kwenu, elizweni elichapha iJordani lisiya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo\x + Hlab. 78.5,6.\x*.
\s Imilayezelo yokucina yeN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Khangela, insuku zakho zokufa sezisondele\x + 31.2,16.\x*; biza uJoshuwa, zimiseni ethenteni lenhlangano ukuze ngimlaye. UMozisi loJoshuwa bahamba-ke, bazimisa ethenteni lenhlangano\x + 31.23. Nani 27.19.\x*.
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakala ethenteni ensikeni yeyezi; lensika yeyezi yema phezu komnyango wethente\x + Eks. 33.9.\x*.
\p
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Khangela, uzalala laboyihlo; lalababantu bazasukuma\x + Eks. 32.6.\x* baphinge ngokulandela onkulunkulu bezizweni belizwe, lapho abaya khona phakathi kwabo\x + Eks. 34.15.\x*, bangitshiye\x + Hlu. 2.12. 10.6,13.\x*, bephule isivumelwano sami engisenze labo\x + 31.20. Hlu. 2.1. Levi 26.15.\x*.
\v 17 Lentukuthelo yami izabavuthela ngalolosuku, ngibatshiye\x + 2 Lan. 15.2. 24.20.\x*, ngibafihlele ubuso bami, ukuze babe yikudla\x + 32.20. Hlab. 30.7. 104.29. Isa. 8.17. 64.7. Hez. 39.23. Isa. 59.2.\x*, behlelwe ngokubi okunengi lezinhlupheko, baze bathi ngalolosuku: Angithi lobububi busehlele ngoba uNkulunkulu wethu kakho phakathi kwethu\x + Nani 14.42.\x*?
\v 18 Lami ngizafihla lokufihla ubuso bami ngalolosuku ngenxa yobubi bonke ababenzileyo, ngoba bephendukele kwabanye onkulunkulu\x + 31.17.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho-ke zibhaleleni lingoma, uyifundise abantwana bakoIsrayeli; uyifake emlonyeni wabo ukuze lingoma ibe yibufakazi kimi obumelene labantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 31.21,26.\x*.
\v 20 Lapho sengibangenisile elizweni engalifungela oyise, eligeleza uchago loluju, sebedlile basutha\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*, bazimuka\x + 32.15.\x*, bazaphendukela kwabanye onkulunkulu, babakhonze\x + 31.18.\x*, bangidelele\x + Nani 14.11,23. 16.30.32.19.\x*, bephule isivumelwano sami\x + 31.20. Hlu. 2.1. Levi 26.15.\x*.
\v 21 Kuzakuthi-ke, nxa sebehlelwe ngokubi okunengi lezinhlupheko, lingoma izaphendula phambi kobuso babo ibe yibufakazi; ngoba kayiyikukhohlakala emlonyeni wenzalo yabo\x + 31.17.\x*. Ngoba ngiyawazi\x + Hos. 5.3. 13.5,6.\x* amacebo abo abawenzayo lamuhla, ngingakabangenisi elizweni engifunge ngalo\x + Gen. 6.5.\x*.
\p
\v 22 UMozisi wasebhala lingoma ngalolosuku, wayifundisa abantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 23 Yasilaya uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni yathi\x + 31.14.\x*: Qina, ume isibindi, ngoba wena uzabangenisa abantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni engabafungela lona\x + 31.6.\x*; lami ngizakuba lawe\x + 31.8.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Kwasekusithi uMozisi eseqedile ukubhala amazwi alumlayo egwalweni, aze aphela\x + 31.9.\x*,
\v 25 uMozisi walaya amaLevi ayethwala umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* esithi\x + 31.9.\x*:
\v 26 Thathani lolugwalo lomlayo, lilubeke eceleni komtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, ukuze lube khona\x + 2 Kho.22.8.\x*, kube yibufakazi obumelene lawe\x + 31.19,21.\x*.
\v 27 Ngoba mina ngiyazi umvukela wakho, lentamo yakho elukhuni; khangelani, ngisaphila lani lamuhla\x + Eks. 32.9.\x*, belingabavukeli beN\nd kosi\nd*; pho, kangakanani emva kokufa kwami\x + 9.7,24.\x*?
\p
\v 28 Buthanisani kimi bonke abadala bezizwe zenu lenduna zenu ukuze ngikhulume lamazwi endlebeni zabo\x + 16.18.\x*, ngibize amazulu lomhlaba ukuba ngabafakazi bamelane labo\x + 30.19. 32.1.\x*.
\v 29 Ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi emva kokufa kwami lizakona lokona, liphambuke endleleni engililaye yona\x + 32.5. Hlu. 2.19. Hos. 9.9.\x*; lizakwehlelwa ngokubi ngensuku ezizayo, ngoba lizakwenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 4.30; Gen.49.1.\x*\nd*, liyithukuthelise ngomsebenzi wezandla zenu\x + 4.25. 9.18. 32.16,21. Dute. 32.19,27. Hlu. 2.12. 1 Sam. 1.6,7.\x*.
\s Ingoma kaMozisi
\p
\v 30 UMozisi wasekhuluma amazwi alingoma endlebeni zebandla lonke lakoIsrayeli, aze aphela.